{"tid":2146260,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（今次我講先）保險業監管局回應美國政府向香港人士施加制裁","createTime":"2020-08-08T12:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T17:25:01.000Z","uid":123606,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ae656563876b50d714b98a47ea1b4c827b834f97","tid":2146260,"uid":123606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:51:17.000Z","msg":"保險業監管局（保監局）正密切注視美國政府於2020年8月7日向一些內地及香港人士施加制裁所帶來的反響。<br />\n<br />\n保監局發言人表示：「在評估這些制裁的潛在影響時，業界人士應全盤考慮他們須面對的法律、業務及商業風險，當中涉及複雜營運事宜，程度因應不同保險公司、保險中介人自身和其海外附屬公司的結構、規模、業務組合而異。首要的是，保監局期望相關公司在制定任何應對措施時，客戶將獲得公平及透明的對待。」<br />\n<br />\nCut鳩佢保單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ia.org.hk/tc/infocenter/press_releases/20200808.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ia.org.hk%2Ftc%2Finfocenter%2Fpress_releases%2F20200808.html&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=2a92fa9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ia.org.hk/tc/infocenter/press_releases/20200808.html</a>"},{"pid":"e7cd9092687fb069f2e042752beee56f496aaf7d","tid":2146260,"uid":123606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:53:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509f4c981c9368d1d834f19ed3d817a3479f55ea","tid":2146260,"uid":80416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:54:56.000Z","msg":"支持保險佬公平及透明地cut你保單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448ec647506216cfc83464ea2167fc831559b6a0","tid":2146260,"uid":123606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:00:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb86be2a47f7ee1ae6e9aabae21afaefd0cba006","tid":2146260,"uid":123606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep